PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FThe causes of an issue which prevented
OL,8,Fa government-backed bank from uniting
OL,9,Ffamily members with deceased loved
OL,10,Fone's financial assets has "been
OL,11,Faddressed", the government has said.
OL,13,FTreasury-backed savings giant NS&I is
OL,14,Fpreparing to pay out hundreds of
OL,15,Fmillions of pounds, after failures
OL,16,Fmeant that bereaved families were
OL,17,Fmissing out on saving posts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FNS&I chief executive Dax Harkins is
OL,8,Falso being replaced by formed HM
OL,9,FRevenue and Customs boss Sir Jim
OL,10,FHarra, in what the pensions minister
OL,11,Fdescribed as a "fresh start".
OL,13,FAddressing MPs on Thursday, Torsten
OL,14,FBell said it was clear National
OL,15,FSavings and Investments (NS&I) had not
OL,16,Fheeded the warnings when Santander
OL,17,Fexperienced similar issues for which
OL,18,Fthe Financial Conduct Authority took
OL,19,Fenforcement action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FBell said the causes affecting the
OL,8,Fbank's ability to trace the families
OL,9,Fof customers who had passed away had
OL,10,Fbeen resolved and that it was now the
OL,11,Fbank's responsibility to contact these
OL,12,Fcustomers.
OL,14,FHe also confirmed that returning
OL,15,Fsavings to bereaved families will not
OL,16,Fhave an effect on taxpayers' money,
OL,17,Finsisting the money being returned to
OL,18,Faffected customers was already
OL,19,Frightfully theirs on account of
OL,20,Fbelonging to their deceased loved ones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FSo what went wrong, and could you be
OL,8,Fowed compensation?
OL,10,FWhat is NS&I?
OL,12,FNS&I is owned by the government, with
OL,13,Fcustomers' savings being managed by
OL,14,Fthe Treasury.
OL,16,FIt is believed to offer a range of
OL,17,Fsavings and investments to more than
OL,18,F24 million customers, including over
OL,19,F22 million Premium Bonds holders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FAs a state-owned bank, the money is
OL,8,Ffully backed by the government with no
OL,9,Fupper limit in case things ever went
OL,10,Fwrong.
OL,12,FBanks not owned by the state generally
OL,13,Finsure your savings up to #85,000.
OL,15,FCompensation paid to customers
OL,16,Ftherefore, comes from the
OL,17,Fgovernment's, and by extension, the
OL,18,Ftaxpayers' pockets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FState-owned banks typically offer
OL,8,Flower interest rates to customers as
OL,9,Fthey prioritise low-risk investments
OL,10,Fand so see less growth.
OL,12,FWhat happened?
OL,14,FMuch of the problem leading to the
OL,15,Fcompensation announced on Thursday
OL,16,Frevolves around NS&I's mishandling of
OL,17,Fmoney owed to bereaved families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FThousands are reported to have had
OL,8,Fprize money from Premium Bonds and
OL,9,Fother money held in accounts of the
OL,10,Fdeceased withheld from them.
OL,12,FThe bank has also been plagued by
OL,13,Ferrors following an IT modernisation
OL,14,Fproject initially dubbed Project
OL,15,FRainbow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FInvestigating this issue, the Public
OL,8,FAccounts Committee said last month:
OL,9,F"It is deeply worrying to see a
OL,10,Fproject in such an important
OL,11,Forganisation so off-track that neither
OL,12,Fthis Committee, or at times the
OL,13,FTreasury itself, could gain an
OL,14,Faccurate sounding on costs and
OL,15,Fprogress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,F"NS&I did not have the skills to run
OL,8,Fthis project successfully to begin
OL,9,Fwith, leaning on expensive consultants
OL,10,Fwhile overseeing a programme which
OL,11,Fstill has yet to bring any meaningful
OL,12,Fbenefits as costs continue to pile up
OL,13,Fand the taxpayer exposed to
OL,14,Funacceptable risks along the way.
OL,16,F"The whole-life cost of this scheme
OL,17,Fwas estimated at #3 billion in 2024.
OL,18,FAs a comparator, the Bank of England's
OL,19,Fearly settlement scheme was renewed in
OL,20,Fa similar timeframe, on time and on
OL,21,Fbudget, at a cost of #431 million."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
