OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIt is believed around 37,000 people
OL,13,Fhave been affected by poor customer
OL,14,Fservice and a mismanagement of their
OL,15,Fmoney.
OL,17,FThe Daily Telegraph reported concerns
OL,18,Fabout money being released and about
OL,19,Fincorrect information.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
