SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FAccording to figures from the
OL,8,FFinancial Ombudsman Service (FOS), 476
OL,9,Fnew complaints were recorded about
OL,10,FNS&I in 2024 related to various
OL,11,Fmatters generally, with 564 new
OL,12,Fcomplaints recorded in 2023.
OL,14,FIn the first half of last year, 151
OL,15,Fcomplaints generally about NS&I were
OL,16,Frecorded by the ombudsman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
