OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FApologising for the problem, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson for the bank said: "We
OL,9,Frecognise that dealing with
OL,10,Fbereavement can be challenging and
OL,11,Fwould like to apologise to anyone who
OL,12,Fhas not received the customer service
OL,13,Ffrom NS&I that they should expect,
OL,14,Fparticularly at such a sensitive time."
OL,16,FWhat has the government said?
OL,26,@pD@aOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FSpeaking in the Commons, pensions
OL,8,Fminister Torsten Bell assured MPs the
OL,9,Fcauses of a tracing issue which
OL,10,Faffected NS&I customers have "been
OL,11,Faddressed and will not affect
OL,12,Fcustomers going forward".
OL,14,FThe pensions minister also told the
OL,15,FCommons that "this issue is about
OL,16,Ftracing, not the security of any
OL,17,Ffunds" held by NS&I, adding that
OL,18,F"savings are 100% safe".
OL,26,@rD@^OUtD@XO]wD@NOUyD@FO]zD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FNS&I is responsible for reuniting
OL,8,Fbeneficiaries with the money they are
OL,9,Fdue, the pensions minister told MPs,
OL,10,Fadding: "There is no need for
OL,11,Findividuals to waste money on a claims
OL,12,Fmanagement company or solicitor."
OL,14,FBell told the Commons: "NS&I has put
OL,15,Fin place a dedicated programme team
OL,16,Fand it's hired an additional 100 staff.
OL,18,F"I have asked them to publish a
OL,19,Fdelivery plan in May detailing how
OL,20,Fthey will take forward this work to
OL,21,Freunite funds with their owners.
OL,26,@rD@IOUtD@aO]vD@XOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,F"This will cover the number of cases
OL,8,Faffected, how NS&I will proactively
OL,9,Fcontact representatives of estates to
OL,10,Fensure they receive the funds they are
OL,11,Fdue, including interest on savings,
OL,12,Fand the compensation that, where
OL,13,Fappropriate, will be paid.
OL,15,F"There is no need for individuals to
OL,16,Fwaste money on a claims management
OL,17,Fcompany or solicitor.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,F"I want to reassure people that the
OL,8,Fonus is not on them but on NS&I to
OL,9,Fact, to contact estate representatives
OL,10,Fand to reconnect beneficiaries with
OL,11,Fthe money they are due."
OL,13,FAre savers owed compensation?
OL,15,FSome reports suggested the resolution
OL,16,Fof NS&I's problems could be
OL,17,Faccompanied by a large bill for the UK
OL,18,Ftaxpayer.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FBell confirmed the bulk of the figures
OL,8,Fbeing talked about was the money
OL,9,Fdeposited by savers, which rightly
OL,10,Fbelonged to their surviving loved
OL,11,Fones, and not taxpayer funds.
OL,13,FWhilst not fleshing out a full
OL,14,Fcompensation scheme for saver's
OL,15,Ftroubles, the pensions minister did
OL,16,Fsay it would be up to NS&I to contact
OL,17,Fthose owed compensation, and that
OL,18,Fusual routes for remuneration were
OL,19,Fopen to consumers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774576986
OL,3,CNS&I 'responsible' for returning
OL,4,Ccustomers' savings - are you owed
OL,5,Ccompensation?
OL,7,FFor some, that will take the form of
OL,8,Fthe interest accrued on their loved
OL,9,Fone's savings whilst they were unable
OL,10,Fto access them.
OL,12,FFor others who pursued legal action to
OL,13,Faccess their funds, or experienced
OL,14,Fother consequences as a result of not
OL,15,Fhaving access to their savings, this
OL,16,Fmay also include compensation for this
OL,17,F"on a case-by-case basis."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
